#. <section class="sutta" id="sn7.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Upāsakavagga"
msgstr "2. Lay Followers"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Devahitasutta"
msgstr "13. With Devahita"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.375"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā vātehābādhiko hoti;"
msgstr "Now at that time the Buddha was afflicted by winds."

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.3"
msgid "āyasmā ca upavāṇo bhagavato upaṭṭhāko hoti."
msgstr "Venerable Upavāṇa was his carer."

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ upavāṇaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Upavāṇa:"

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.5"
msgid "“iṅgha me tvaṃ, upavāṇa, uṇhodakaṃ jānāhī”ti."
msgstr "“Please, Upavāṇa, find some hot water for me.”"

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.6"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā upavāṇo bhagavato paṭissutvā nivāsetvā "
"pattacīvaramādāya yena devahitassa brāhmaṇassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā tuṇhībhūto ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"“Yes, sir,” replied Upavāṇa. He robed up, and, taking his bowl and robe, "
"went to the house of the brahmin Devahita, and stood silently to one side."

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.7"
msgid ""
"Addasā kho devahito brāhmaṇo āyasmantaṃ upavāṇaṃ tuṇhībhūtaṃ ekamantaṃ "
"ṭhitaṃ."
msgstr "Devahita saw him standing there"

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.8"
msgid "Disvāna āyasmantaṃ upavāṇaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "and addressed him in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.175"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:2.1"
msgid "“Tuṇhībhūto bhavaṃ tiṭṭhaṃ,"
msgstr "“Silent stands the Master,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:2.2"
msgid "muṇḍo saṅghāṭipāruto;"
msgstr "shaven, wrapped in his outer robe."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:2.3"
msgid "Kiṃ patthayāno kiṃ esaṃ,"
msgstr "What do you want? What are you looking for?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:2.4"
msgid "kiṃ nu yācitumāgato”ti."
msgstr "What have you come here to ask for?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.376"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:3.1"
msgid "“Arahaṃ sugato loke,"
msgstr "“The perfected one, the Holy One in the world,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:3.2"
msgid "vātehābādhiko muni;"
msgstr "the sage is afflicted by winds."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:3.3"
msgid "Sace uṇhodakaṃ atthi,"
msgstr "If there’s hot water,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:3.4"
msgid "munino dehi brāhmaṇa."
msgstr "give it to the sage, brahmin."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:4.1"
msgid "Pūjito pūjaneyyānaṃ,"
msgstr "I wish to bring it to the one"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:4.2"
msgid "sakkareyyāna sakkato;"
msgstr "who is esteemed by the estimable,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: apaceyyānaṃ → apacaneyyānaṃ (si) | apacineyyānaṃ (s1-3, km, pts2)
msgctxt "sn7.13:4.3"
msgid "Apacito apaceyyānaṃ,"
msgstr "honored by the honorable,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:4.4"
msgid "tassa icchāmi hātave”ti."
msgstr "venerated by the venerable.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:5.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho devahito brāhmaṇo uṇhodakassa kājaṃ purisena gāhāpetvā phāṇitassa "
"ca puṭaṃ āyasmato upavāṇassa pādāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then Devahita had a man fetch a carrying-pole with hot water. He also "
"presented Upavāṇa with a jar of molasses."

#. VAR: nhāpetvā → nahāpetvā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn7.13:5.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā upavāṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ uṇhodakena nhāpetvā uṇhodakena phāṇitaṃ āloletvā bhagavato "
"pādāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Upavāṇa went up to the Buddha and bathed him with the hot "
"water. Then he stirred molasses into hot water and presented it to the "
"Buddha."

msgctxt "sn7.13:5.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavato ābādho paṭippassambhi."
msgstr "Then the Buddha’s illness died down."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:6.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho devahito brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then the brahmin Devahita went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings "
"with him."

msgctxt "sn7.13:6.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side,"

msgctxt "sn7.13:6.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho devahito brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "and addressed the Buddha in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.377"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:7.1"
msgid "“Kattha dajjā deyyadhammaṃ,"
msgstr "“Where should you give an available gift?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:7.2"
msgid "kattha dinnaṃ mahapphalaṃ;"
msgstr "Where is a gift very fruitful?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:7.3"
msgid "Kathañhi yajamānassa,"
msgstr "How does one who is donating"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:7.4"
msgid "kathaṃ ijjhati dakkhiṇā”ti."
msgstr "ensure the success of their teacher’s offering?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:8.1"
msgid "“Pubbenivāsaṃ yo vedī,"
msgstr "“One who knows their past lives,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:8.2"
msgid "saggāpāyañca passati;"
msgstr "and sees heaven and places of loss,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:8.3"
msgid "Atho jātikkhayaṃ patto,"
msgstr "and has attained the ending of rebirth,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:8.4"
msgid "abhiññāvosito muni."
msgstr "that sage has perfect insight."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:9.1"
msgid "Ettha dajjā deyyadhammaṃ,"
msgstr "Here you should give an available gift;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:9.2"
msgid "ettha dinnaṃ mahapphalaṃ;"
msgstr "what’s given here is very fruitful."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:9.3"
msgid "Evañhi yajamānassa,"
msgstr "That’s how a sponsor of sacrifices"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:9.4"
msgid "evaṃ ijjhati dakkhiṇā”ti."
msgstr "ensures the success of their teacher’s offering.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.13:10.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, devahito brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, the brahmin Devahita said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.13:10.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama …"

msgctxt "sn7.13:10.3"
msgid ""
"upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life.”"
